text:
Photo: Via @juleshough.

As if you needed another perfect Instagram post pushing you to go to the gym this evening. Laich may be the professional athlete in the family, but it looks like Hough can give him a run for his money. And we're back to that gorgeous beach. Even with that coast in the background, Hough still steals the focus.
